/news/26810\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>刚刚</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">千问 3.6 正式发布：100 万长上下文，硬刚 Claude Code</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">阿里发布新一代大语言模型Qwen3.6-Plus，被誉为当前最强国产编程模型。相比3.5版本性能显著提升，在多项编程评测中位居国产首位，整体能力接近国际标杆Claude系列。该模型在前端开发、复杂仓库任务等方面展现出高度自主化能力。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"千问 3.6 正式发布：100 万长上下文，硬刚 Claude Code\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/thumb/202504151007232048_2.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: 德国民众担忧 AI 深度伪造风险超九成\" href=\"/news/26809\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>刚刚</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">德国民众担忧 AI 深度伪造风险超九成</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">德国民调显示，超九成受访者对AI深度伪造感到忧虑，其中过半认为风险“非常高”。担忧主要集中于难以辨别AI生成内容。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"德国民众担忧 AI 深度伪造风险超九成\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/thumb/202305301503482001_2.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: 智谱发布 GLM-5V-Turbo：给 AI 智能体安上“火眼金睛”\" href=\"/news/26807\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>刚刚</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">智谱发布 GLM-5V-Turbo：给 AI 智能体安上“火眼金睛”</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">智谱发布多模态编程模型GLM-5V-Turbo，具备视觉理解能力，可将设计稿、网页界面等视觉信息转化为代码，实现AI Agent从字符到视觉的感知延伸。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"智谱发布 GLM-5V-Turbo：给 AI 智能体安上“火眼金睛”\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/thumb/202406051435016830_1.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: 中国广电联合会演员委员会发布声明:严禁未经授权的AI换脸与影视素材魔改\" href=\"/news/26806\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>刚刚</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">中国广电联合会演员委员会发布声明:严禁未经授权的AI换脸与影视素材魔改</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">中国广播电视社会组织联合会演员委员会发布声明，针对AI换脸、声纹克隆及未经授权抓取数据训练模型等七类AI侵权行为明确禁止，强调即使标注“非商用”等字样也不能免责，侵权主体需承担全部法律责任。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"中国广电联合会演员委员会发布声明:严禁未经授权的AI换脸与影视素材魔改\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/thumb/202307261637383850_8.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: AI 编程进入“靠谱”时代：通义实验室正式发布 Qwen3.6-Plus\" href=\"/news/26805\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>刚刚</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">AI 编程进入“靠谱”时代：通义实验室正式发布 Qwen3.6-Plus</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">通义实验室发布Qwen3.6-Plus模型，聚焦解决智能体编程中“任务执行不稳”问题。该模型通过阿里云百炼API开放调用，核心升级在于融合深度逻辑推理、海量记忆与精准执行，显著提升编码能力，尤其在前端页面生成、代码修复及终端自动化场景表现卓越。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"AI 编程进入“靠谱”时代：通义实验室正式发布 Qwen3.6-Plus\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://upload.chinaz.com/2026/0402/6391074315066537525878796.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: 微信强化 “AI 魔改” 视频治理，处置违规短视频内容 3800 条\" href=\"/news/26804\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>刚刚</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">微信强化 “AI 魔改” 视频治理，处置违规短视频内容 3800 条</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">微信平台发布公告，加强对“AI魔改”视频的监管，以遏制部分账号滥用AI工具对经典影视剧和动画片进行颠覆性篡改的问题，维护网络信息传播秩序。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"微信强化 “AI 魔改” 视频治理，处置违规短视频内容 3800 条\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/thumb/201908071152532306_3.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: 快手可灵AI月活突破 780 万，登顶全球移动端AI视频“新王座”\" href=\"/news/26803\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>刚刚</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">快手可灵AI月活突破 780 万，登顶全球移动端AI视频“新王座”</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">快手旗下可灵AI在全球移动端市场表现突出，尤其在OpenAI关闭Sora后，凭借高用户黏性与口碑成为全球最受关注的视频模型。数据显示，可灵AI月活跃用户达780万，远超Sora的470万，呈现断层领先优势。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"快手可灵AI月活突破 780 万，登���全球移动端AI视频“新王座”\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/thumb/201907082355045789_6.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: 国产 LLM 工具链再升级！开源 LLMOps 平台 Maxkb4j v2.6.0 正式发布\" href=\"/news/26802\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>刚刚</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">国产 LLM 工具链再升级！开源 LLMOps 平台 Maxkb4j v2.6.0 正式发布</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">Maxkb4j v2.6.0版本发布，作为开源LLMOps平台，本次更新强化了技能扩展、安全鉴权与系统稳定性。核心功能包括新增Shell工具与系统消息集成，并实现了Webhook鉴权，为开发者提供了更强大的LLM工作流与RAG能力开发支持。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"国产 LLM 工具链再升级！开源 LLMOps 平台 Maxkb4j v2.6.0 正式发布\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/thumb/202405161743122232_2.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: 蚂蚁AI安全实验室开源ClawAegis，破解OpenClaw类智能体安全难题\" href=\"/news/26801\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>刚刚</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">蚂蚁AI安全实验室开源ClawAegis，破解OpenClaw类智能体安全难题</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">4月2日，蚂蚁集团与清华大学联合开源ClawAegis，这是首个覆盖OpenClaw全生命周期的安全防御插件，旨在系统性解决其安全与可靠性风险。该插件为自主智能体提供多维度、轻量化、即时干预的原生防护能力。随着OpenClaw等开源智能体框架的普及，其自动化能力背后的安全风险日益显现，包括skill投毒、记忆数据污染、意图被恶意诱导及执行高危操作等。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"蚂蚁AI安全实验室开源ClawAegis，破解OpenClaw类智能体安全难题\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/thumb/202309121506505395_0.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章:  腾讯WorkBuddy突发登录崩溃：官方致歉并补偿受影响用户 1000 积分\" href=\"/news/26800\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>4  分钟前</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\"> 腾讯WorkBuddy突发登录崩溃：官方致歉并补偿受影响用户 1000 积分</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">腾讯AI协作工具WorkBuddy于4月2日上午突发大规模登录故障，部分用户遭遇页面错误、无法登录等问题。腾讯云随后致歉并公布补偿方案，承诺向受影响国内用户发放1000Credits积分，预计两日内到账。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\" 腾讯WorkBuddy突发登录崩溃：官方致歉并补偿受影响用户 1000 积分\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/thumb/202305221413351383_9.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: 谷歌开源大模型 Gemma 4 官宣在即：参数量翻 4 倍\" href=\"/news/26799\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>15  分钟前</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">谷歌开源大模型 Gemma 4 官宣在即：参数量翻 4 倍</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">谷歌DeepMind暗示将发布新一代开源大模型Gemma 4，规格大幅升级至120B参数，挑战本地运行极限，试图在全球开源大模型市场夺回话语权。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"谷歌开源大模型 Gemma 4 官宣在即：参数量翻 4 倍\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/thumb/202402221038136007_0.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: 国内首个任务型医疗AI面世：百度健康发布“有医助理”\" href=\"/news/26798\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>15  分钟前</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">国内首个任务型医疗AI面世：百度健康发布“有医助理”</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">百度健康推出国内首个医生任务型AI产品“有医助理”，标志着医疗AI从资料检索迈向深度参与临床与科研的执行阶段。该产品融合权威医学检索与AI执行能力，通过Claw框架实现自主处理，为医生提供精准知识支撑，助力提升工作效率。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"国内首个任务型医疗AI面世：百度健康发布“有医助理”\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/202307181418295015_2.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: IBM发布Granite 4.0 3B Vision：企业级文档数据提取的新利器\" href=\"/news/26797\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>18  分钟前</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">IBM发布Granite 4.0 3B Vision：企业级文档数据提取的新利器</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">IBM发布Granite 4.0 3B Vision视觉语言模型，拥有30亿参数，专为企业级复杂文档数据提取优化。该模型针对金融、法律、医疗等行业非结构化数据处理难题，在复杂表格、扫描件及多模态布局文档中表现突出，通过结合视觉理解与语言生成，精准识别并提取关键信息。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"IBM发布Granite 4.0 3B Vision：企业级文档数据提取的新利器\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/201811151614001174_41.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: Anthropic 测试“龙虾” Conway：支持独立 UI、Webhook 唤醒与自定义扩展标准\" href=\"/news/26796\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>32  分钟前</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">Anthropic 测试“龙虾” Conway：支持独立 UI、Webhook 唤醒与自定义扩展标准</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">Anthropic正为Claude开发常驻代理Conway，打造独立运行、始终在线的智能环境。它将拥有独立UI，超越传统聊天界面，作为代理工作空间运行。Conway可直接操作浏览器、连接外部工具，并集成代码功能，实现深度任务处理与代码执行。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"Anthropic 测试“龙虾” Conway：支持独立 UI、Webhook 唤醒与自定义扩展标准\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/thumb/202603101646537572_2.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: 阶跃星辰推出 Step 3.5 Flash 系列，面向所有 Step Plan 用户开放\" href=\"/news/26795\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>34  分钟前</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">阶跃星辰推出 Step 3.5 Flash 系列，面向所有 Step Plan 用户开放</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">阶跃星辰发布Step 3.5 Flash系列模型，旨在实现高性能与低成本的平衡。该系列针对移动端和高频交互场景优化，在保持逻辑理解能力的同时，显著提升响应速度并降低推理成本。目前Step Plan用户可优先体验。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"阶跃星辰推出 Step 3.5 Flash 系列，面向所有 Step Plan 用户开放\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/202305091556160776_8.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: 系统级深度融合！中兴联手字节跳动：新一代豆包 AI 手机定档 Q2\" href=\"/news/26794\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>55  分钟前</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">系统级深度融合！中兴联手字节跳动：新一代豆包 AI 手机定档 Q2</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">中兴通讯与字节跳动合作的新一代豆包AI手机预计2026年第二季度末发布，旨在将AI进化为具备自主行动能力的智能体。此前工程机曾被炒至3.6万元，市场期待极高。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"系统级深度融合！中兴联手字节跳动：新一代豆包 AI 手机定档 Q2\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/thumb/202309130951177828_0.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: 航旅纵横上线AI预订机酒功能: 告别手动筛选 支持全自动“说”订机酒\" href=\"/news/26793\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>1  小时前</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">航旅纵横上线AI预订机酒功能: 告别手动筛选 支持全自动“说”订机酒</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">航旅纵横App推出“AI预订机酒”功能，实现智能助手从对话交互到业务执行的升级。用户通过自然语言输入需求，系统即可自动搜索、筛选并推荐机票酒店，匹配最优行程方案。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"航旅纵横上线AI预订机酒功能: 告别手动筛选 支持全自动“说”订机酒\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/thumb/201902131139582742_3.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: 千问 AI 眼镜迎来首次 OTA 升级，增强多项生活服务功能\" href=\"/news/26792\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>3  小时前</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">千问 AI 眼镜迎来首次 OTA 升级，增强多项生活服务功能</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">千问AI眼镜首次OTA升级，新增“多人对话AI克隆同传”功能，可精准克隆发言者音色，实现低延迟同声传译，打破跨语言沟通边界，提升商务洽谈和跨国旅行体验。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"千问 AI 眼镜迎来首次 OTA 升级，增强多项生活服务功能\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://upload.chinaz.com/2026/0402/6391072678558158362145505.png\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: 芯片设计进入AI自进化时代：Cognichip获 6000 万美元融资\" href=\"/news/26791\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>3  小时前</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">芯片设计进入AI自进化时代：Cognichip获 6000 万美元融资</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">初创公司Cognichip获6000万美元A轮融资，致力于用AI技术革新半导体设计。其“用AI设计AI芯片”理念旨在解决高性能硬件研发周期长、成本高的问题。传统芯片开发需数百工程师耗时数年，而该公司的AI系统可通过深度学习自动优化电路布局，大幅缩短研发时间。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"芯片设计进入AI自进化时代：Cognichip获 6000 万美元融资\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/thumb/202304231132173466_7.jpg\"/></div></div></a><a class=\"flex group justify-between md:flex-row flex-col-reverse hover:bg-[#F0F3FA] rounded-lg md:p-4 py-2 px-0 group\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"阅读文章: 蚂蚁数科DTClaw开启内测:定位专业级AI智能体赛道\" href=\"/news/26790\"><div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 space-y-2 flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 flex items-center space-x-1\"><span>3  小时前</span><span>.</span><span class=\"font-light\">AIbase</span></div><div class=\"w-full\"><h3 class=\"line-clamp-2 md:text-xl text-lg text-surface-800\">蚂蚁数科DTClaw开启内测:定位专业级AI智能体赛道</h3></div><div class=\"py-2 hidden md:block\"><div class=\"text-[15px] line-clamp-2 text-surface-500\">蚂蚁数科推出专业AI智能体DTClaw，开启内测。该产品定位“专业型”AI，面向金融专家、数据分析师等深度专业人群，提供全天候专属服务。不同于通用型助手，DTClaw强调“原生专家”属性，旨在满足专业领域的高阶需求。</div></div></div><div class=\"w-40 h-32 ml-10 md:block hidden rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-transparent animate-pulse object-cover w-full h-full transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out transform group-hover:scale-110\"><img alt=\"蚂蚁数科DTClaw开启内测:定位专业级AI智能体赛道\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"transition-opacity duration-300 object-cover opacity-0\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://pic.chinaz.com/picmap/thumb/202603101646528492_0.jpg\"/></div></div></a></div><div class=\"py-6 text-center invisible\"><div class=\"inline-block h-8 w-8 animate-spin rounded-full border-4 border-solid border-current border-r-transparent align-[-0.125em] motion-reduce:animate-[spin_1.5s_linear_infinite]\"></div><p class=\"mt-2 text-gray-500\">加载中...</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></main></div><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-17ca4f40a8347343.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n4:I[9766,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n5:I[98924,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n6:I[31021,[\\\"902\\\",\\\"static/chunks/902-27772842be6816ea.js\\\",\\\"2619\\\",\\\"static/chunks/2619-04bc32f026a0d946.js\\\",\\\"6350\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/%5Blang%5D/news/not-found-98a47e19893b0d61.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n8:I[24431,[],\\\"OutletB