{"type":"message","id":"8ac1fb11","parentId":"f19a49e4","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:53:34.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The file has been written. Now I should also check if there's a need to update the MEMORY.md or any other related files. Let me also check the existing memory file to see if it needs to be updated with this new information.\n\nActually, the task was completed - I successfully:\n1. Read the skill file for web search (it wasn't available at the expected path)\n2. Found an alternative way to get AI industry news via web fetch\n3. Compiled 5 key industry trends from the latest 2026 data\n4. Written the complete markdown content to the target file /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\nThe task is complete. I should summarize what was accomplished.","thinkingSignature":"311b433b05e5f54a7dd33b4e3bcffb941d9327a7f3cb1ebcf440e354c2557ee5"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n已完成子Agent任务，继续搜索并整理了2026年最新行业动态。\n\n**完成情况：**\n\n从AIbase、AIbase基地等科技媒体获取了2026年4月2日的最新AI行业资讯，整理了5条关键信息：\n\n1. **AI大模型编程能力跃升**：Qwen3.6-Plus发布，100万Token上下文，国产编程模型进入\"靠谱\"时代\n2. **AI Agent向专业化进化**：蚂蚁DTClaw、百度\"有医助理\"密集发布，从通用助手转向垂直行业专家\n3. **AI视频生成中国领跑**：快手可灵AI月活780万，超Sora成为全球移动端AI视频第一\n4. **LLMOps工具链完善**：开源Maxkb4j v2.6.0发布，企业级AI应用底座加固\n5. **AI安全框架正式建立**：蚂蚁开源ClawAegis，首个覆盖OpenClaw全生命周期的安全防御插件\n\n**输出文件：** `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`（2652字节）\n\n每条信息均包含标题、核心内容、启示，并附有行业关键词追踪表。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":81062,"output":407,"cacheRead":42506,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123975,"cost":{"input":0.0243186,"output":0.0004883999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0012751799999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02608218}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775141601919}}
